  "name": "The Ixian Grand & All Suites - Adults Only Hotel",
  "description": "The Ixian Grand & All Suites - Adults Only Hotel, is a five-star beachfront resort on the West coast of Rhodes that offers breathtaking views of Ixia beach and the Aegean Sea. The resort provides relaxing and dreamy experiences in a luxurious setting! Our guests can enjoy several facilities such as large swimming pools, a la carte restaurants, a large Spa, a gym and many more. The resort consists of its main building and the garden complex. The main building features 124 deluxe guestrooms with garden or sea view and with or without a Spa Tub. The garden complex features 122 spacious and comfortable guestrooms with views to the garden or the quiet street in front of the hotel. The Ixian Grand & All Suites - Adults Only Hotel is ideally located just 6km away from Rhodes Town and 7km from the International Airport “Diagoras”, making it the ideal base for you to explore the endless beauties of Rhodes island. It is just few minutes away by car from the protected by UNESCO World Heritage Monument, “Medieval City of Rhodes” and the Mount Filerimos with its breathtaking panoramic views.",
